name: The Film Log I - Genesis Collection
description:
Film Log is a collection of traditional film photographs that aims to capture and archive fleeting present moments. All photographs are shot in traditional 35mm analog film, Minolta SRT-100 and minted as limited edition NFT. (Enter full screen to see more details.)


This is also a part of the P A R A D O X Collective, that shows the contradicting harmony of traditional and digital media.


Published Circa February 2016

(If you are a verified owner of this NFT, you may get your unlockable content of digital published copy along with several assets by sending a DM to @glaedrx on twitter.)
